                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p37h1f675/manifest/annotation/p4",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>back, et afres<add>?</add>? <sic>our</sic> turn will come I presume<lb/> and we shall\n                have northern invincibles<lb/> occupying <placeName>Montreal</placeName> n'est ce\n                pas?</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">When we meet we can discuss<lb/> these weighty matters. Till then\n                things, I presume<lb/> will go their way uninfluenced by what we<lb/> may say, so\n                why vex ourselves therewith<add>?</add></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">During my recent visit to <placeName>England</placeName><lb/> I\n                found that it was rather more common than I<lb/> expected, to <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                    >exchange</hi> publications. So if every you<lb/> want a few English's,\n                Calendars, &amp;c on these terms (with<lb/> the usual discount, I shall be glad to\n                supply you,<lb/> As I am sending on a parcel to <persName>Miss Gratz</persName>, I\n                will<lb/> enclose you a few numbers of Part 1 of Sanatary<add>?</add><lb/>\n                Institutions, recently put in paper covers which you<lb/> perhaps could circulate\n                without much trouble<lb/> among your friends Jewish or Christian—selling<lb/> price\n                25 cents a copy, with 20% off commission.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have now pretty well covered my<lb/> paper, and must therefore bid\n                you adieu for the<lb/> present. <persName>Mrs De Sola</persName> and family\n                untie<lb/> in kind regards and with best wishes</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">I remain yours truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Abraham de Sola</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>May I trouble you to send up to<lb/>\n                <persName>Miss Gratz</persName> the copy<lb/> Sanatary<add>?</add> Institutions and\n                parcel enclosed no doubt<lb/> you can always summons a <add>?</add><lb/>\n                <add>?</add>evil at your <add>?</add></p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p37h1f675/canvas/p4"
                }
              ]
